ckground-color:#FFFFFF;color:#393939;font-family:arial;font-size:17.7777786254883px;&quot;&gt;\r\n		据说惯用左脑思考的人看到这张图一直是顺时针旋转，&lt;br /&gt;\r\n惯用右脑的人看到一直是逆时针旋转，&lt;br /&gt;\r\n智商突破天际的人，会看到顺逆旋转，你呢？\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#393939;font-family:arial;font-size:17.7777786254883px;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#E36C09;&quot;&gt;No.7&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18.1818180084229px;&quot;&gt;【测试眼力】&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#393939;font-family:arial;font-size:17.7777786254883px;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/5MI19JibTs4Ou03ibLLfmuOu9tzOXZe7OWzvf3NGgdWXreWW6sOQUiaU92oYxG3MdOvFxHet6B4ibLTe9BLVX4AUeg/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#393939;font-family:arial;font-size:17.7777786254883px;&quot;&gt;\r\n		这幅图，虽然看上去有点可怕，&lt;br /&gt;\r\n不过回过神来想想，还真是有创意。&lt;br /&gt;\r\n你能看到几种动物？&lt;br /&gt;\r\n据说有人看到30种哦。&lt;br /&gt;\r\n答案：&lt;br /&gt;\r\n0-10，超级近视。&lt;br /&gt;\r\n11-20，正常视力。&lt;br /&gt;\r\n21-30，你就是放大镜。&lt;br /&gt;\r\n30以上，膜拜大神。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#393939;font-family:arial;font-size:17.7777786254883px;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#393939;font-family:arial;font-size:17.7777786254883px;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#E36C09;&quot;&gt;No.8&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18.1818180084229px;&quot;&gt;【枪口指向你】&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#393939;font-family:arial;font-size:17.7777786254883px;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; height=&quot;880&quot; src=&quot;http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V10O3Fob0sSnOp/uWEdoK8Z.8hKObWcbUoM26f7ZE0lUREjxdXR*HJWuS